Race.SpecificTitle: Cons. School Dist. No. 5 -- 4.01 Mills - SB - 10 Yrs.
Race.SummaryText:
CONSOLIDATED SCHOOL DISTRICT NO. 5 PROPOSITION
(MILLAGE RENEWAL)

SUMMARY:  10 YEAR, 4.01 MILLS PROPERTY TAX RENEWAL FOR GIVING ADDITIONAL SUPPORT TO THE PUBLIC SCHOOLS OF THE DISTRICT, INCLUDING, BUT NOT LIMITED TO, REPAIRING, MAINTAINING AND REPLACING EQUIPMENT FOR SCHOOLS IN CONSOLIDATED SCHOOL DISTRICT NO. 5.
Race.FullText: Shall Consolidated School District No. 5 of the Parish of Catahoula, State of Louisiana (the "District"), levy a special tax of four and one hundredth (4.01) mills on all the property subject to taxation in the District (an estimated $19,000 reasonably expected at this time to be collected from the levy of the tax for an entire year) for a period of ten (10) years, beginning with the year 2008 and ending with the year 2017, for the purpose of giving additional support to the public schools of the District, including, but not limited to, repairing, maintaining and replacing equipment for schools in the District?

Race.SpecificTitle: Fire Protection Dist.No.1 -- 6.23 Mill - BOC - 10 Yrs.
Race.SummaryText:
FIRE PROTECTION DISTRICT NO. 1 PROPOSITION
(TAX CONTINUATION)

SUMMARY:  10 YEARS, 6.23 MILLS PROPERTY TAX CONTINUATION FOR ACQUIRING, CONSTRUCTING, IMPROVING, MAINTAINING AND OPERATING FIRE PROTECTION FACILITIES AND EQUIPMENT, PURCHASING FIRE TRUCKS AND OTHER FIRE FIGHTING EQUIPMENT AND PAYING THE COST OF OBTAINING WATER FOR FIRE PROTECTION PURPOSES, INCLUDING CHARGES FOR FIRE HYDRANT RENTALS AND SERVICE.
Race.FullText: Shall Fire Protection District No. 1 of the Parish of Catahoula, State of Louisiana (the "District"), continue to levy a special tax of six and twenty-three hundredths (6.23) mills on all property subject to taxation in the District (an estimated $12,000 reasonably expected at this time to be collected from the levy of the tax for an entire year) for a period of ten (10) years, beginning with the year 2008 and ending with the year 2017, for the purpose of acquiring, constructing, improving, maintaining and operating fire protection facilities and equipment, purchasing fire trucks and other fire fighting equipment and paying the cost of obtaining water for fire protection purposes, including charges for fire hydrant rentals and service?

Race.SpecificTitle: Fire Protection Dist.No.5 -- 10 Mills - BOC - 10 Yrs.
Race.SummaryText:
FIRE PROTECTION DISTRICT NO. 5 PROPOSITION
(MILLAGE RENEWAL)

SUMMARY:  10 YEARS, 10 MILLS PROPERTY TAX RENEWAL FOR ACQUIRING, CONSTRUCTING, IMPROVING, MAINTAINING AND/OR OPERATING FIRE PROTECTION FACILITIES AND EQUIPMENT IN AND FOR FIRE PROTECTION DISTRICT NO. 5 AND PAYING THE COST OF OBTAINING WATER FOR FIRE PROTECTION PURPOSES.
Race.FullText: Shall Fire Protection District No. 5 of the Parish of Catahoula, State of Louisiana (the "District"), levy a special tax of ten (10) mills on all the property subject to taxation in the District for a period of ten (10) years, beginning with the year 2008 and ending the year 2017 (an estimated $18,000 reasonably expected at this time to be collected from the levy of the tax for an entire year), for the purpose of acquiring, constructing, improving, maintaining and/or operating fire protection facilities and equipment in and for the District and paying the cost of obtaining water for fire protection purposes?
